3 national origin, religion, or gender identity.
4 (2) "State or local government agency" means:
5 (a) any branch, department, office, board, bureau, commission, agency, university unit, college, or
6 other instrumentality of state government; or
7 (b) a county, city, town, school district, or other unit of local government and any instrumentality of
8 local government.
9
10 NEW SECTION. Section 3. Codification instruction. [Sections 1 through 2] are intended to be
11 codified as a new chapter in Title 49, and the provisions of Title 49 apply to [sections 1 through 2].
